Class JPATomcatSessionCustomizer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.persistence.config.SessionCustomizer

    public class JPATomcatSessionCustomizer
extends Object
implements org.eclipse.persistence.config.SessionCustomizer
    Tomcat requires java:/comp/env/ prefix for JNDI datasource but not Glassfish. So this class, try to connect to given datasource, and if it doesn't work it add the prefix to jndi lookup name.
